{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"98010-le-porridge","title":"Le Porridge","description":"Mom is away and Dad is making the morning porridge.","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Patricia Roth","Translators withoutBorders"],"illustrators":["Catherine Groenewald"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/98010-le-porridge"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/151769/size3/773091332b87122b8e66a39000540408.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/151769/size6/773091332b87122b8e66a39000540408.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141850/size6/e55b0727ba90dd40084f930533fd971d.jpg","text":"Zama se prépare pour aller à l'école.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141851/size6/e1df198db2dc8610dc52fe6f70df0991.jpg","text":"Papa prépare du porridge pour le petit déjeûner.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141852/size6/082cd48198413faea76cc09af2bc42af.jpg","text":"“C'est maman qui fait le meilleur porridge!” dit Zama.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141853/size6/55704ee979d4147643863f81a0ef5053.jpg","text":"Le porridge permet à Zama de faire le plein d'énergie avant d'aller à l'école.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141856/size6/a5bcd114b1d1bd50a7a3a756791aba84.jpg","text":"Le porridge est prêt.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141859/size6/b2a21bf90017ecf21c0a358d16a428de.jpg","text":"Papa verse le lait avec amour.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141860/size6/a2b682f2087cd8498847783ca32ca7b6.jpg","text":"“Papa, je pense qu'il n'y a pas assez de sucre dans ce porridge”, dit Zama.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141861/size6/7aac4c2874c843847c1747d0b5f87132.jpg","text":"“Le porridge de maman a meilleur goût que celui de papa”, pense Zama.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141862/size6/e2ac152253964a4c3b543eef15bd33b6.jpg","text":"“Papa est-ce que je pourrais avoir plus de sucre s'il te plaît?” demande Zama.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141863/size6/6f520232f273f90f4df1c89c45e455bd.jpg","text":"Papa donne plus de sucre à Zama.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141864/size6/7e74af661b7abf1979c707ade452a399.jpg","text":"“Berk! Papa! Tu as mis du sel dans mon porridge!”","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141865/size6/1a8f793015f676dea123007a291092da.jpg","text":"“Dit papa, quand est-ce qu'elle rentre maman?” demande Zama.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":116}}